FORMULA_TEXT:
/*************************************************************************************
FORMULA NAME	: Biweekly
FORMULA TYPE	: Flow Schedule
DESCRIPTION	: Formula to return NEXT_SCHEDULED_DATE with 14 days frequency
NEXT_SCHEDULED_DATE - This will be a date time value with yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss format.
***************************************************************************************/

/* Inputs  */
INPUTS ARE SUBMISSION_DATE(DATE), SCHEDULED_DATE(DATE)

/* Calculations */
NEXT_SCHEDULED_DATE = ADD_DAYS(SCHEDULED_DATE,14)

/* Returns */
RETURN NEXT_SCHEDULED_DATE

/* End Formula Text */
